(1, 2, 3, 4, '', '<strong>How to use:</strong><br><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul,<br></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart.<br></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot,<br></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy,<br></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence,<br></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; that I neglect my talents. I should be incapable of drawing a single stroke<br></div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; at the present moment; and yet I feel that I never was a greater artist than now.', '', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '', '2017-05-19 00:52:40', '2017-05-19 00:52:40'),
